{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-21-DeadLock-4/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"deadlock-detection\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deadlock-detection\" aria-label=\"deadlock detection permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌deadlock detection</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락을 막지 않음</li>\n<li>주기적으로 데드락 발생을 확인</li>\n<li>Resource allocation graph(RAG)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"rag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rag\" aria-label=\"rag permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖RAG</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락 검출을 위해 사용</li>\n<li>directed, bipartite graph</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/92ea733c-bd71-4b0d-bc2f-c449fa0cd9a6/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"graph-reduction\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#graph-reduction\" aria-label=\"graph reduction permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖graph reduction</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>주어진 RAG에서 edge를 하나씩 지워가는 방법</li>\n<li>completely reduced : 모든 edge가 지워진 상태, deadlock이 없다는 의미</li>\n<li>irreducible : 지울수 없는 edge가 남아있는 상태, deadlock이 있다는 의미</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"edge-지우는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#edge-%EC%A7%80%EC%9A%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"edge 지우는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>edge 지우는 방법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>unblocked process : 필요한 자원을 모두 받을 수 있는 프로세스</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>unblocked process가 가지고 있는 edge를 모두 지운다.</li>\n<li>unblocked process가 없을 때까지 반복</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"deadlock-avoidance-vs-detection\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deadlock-avoidance-vs-detection\" aria-label=\"deadlock avoidance vs detection permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌deadlock avoidance vs detection</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>deadlock avoidance</p>\n<ul>\n<li>최악의 경우를 대비해 미리 데드락을 막는 방법</li>\n<li>데드락이 발생하지 않는다</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>deadlock detection</p>\n<ul>\n<li>최선의 경우를 생각</li>\n<li>데드락 발생시 recovery가 필요</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"deadlock-recovery\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deadlock-recovery\" aria-label=\"deadlock recovery permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌deadlock recovery</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락이 발생했을 때, 데드락을 해결하는 방법</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"deadlock-termination\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deadlock-termination\" aria-label=\"deadlock termination permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖deadlock termination</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락이 발생한 프로세스를 종료시키는 방법</li>\n<li>강제 종료된 프로세스는 이후 재시작</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"termination-cost-model\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#termination-cost-model\" aria-label=\"termination cost model permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>termination cost model</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락이 발생했을 때, 종료시킬 프로세스를 선택하는 방법</li>\n<li>고려 요소\n<ul>\n<li>종류</li>\n<li>총 수행시간</li>\n<li>남은 수행시간</li>\n<li>종료비용</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"resource-preemption\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#resource-preemption\" aria-label=\"resource preemption permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖resource preemption</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락 상태 해결 위해 선점할 자원을 선택</li>\n<li>선정 된 자원을 가지고 있는 프로세스를 종료시키고 자원을 빼앗음</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"preemption-cost-model\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#preemption-cost-model\" aria-label=\"preemption cost model permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>preemption cost model</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>선점할 자원을 선택하는 방법</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"checkpoint-restart-method\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#checkpoint-restart-method\" aria-label=\"checkpoint restart method permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖checkpoint-restart method</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>데드락 recovery에서 프로세스는 항상 종료된다</li>\n<li>프로세스의 수행 중 특정 지점마다 context를 저장</li>\n<li>rollback : 데드락이 발생했을 때, 저장된 context로 되돌림</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#deadlock-detection\">📌deadlock detection</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#rag\">📖RAG</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#graph-reduction\">📖graph reduction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#edge-%EC%A7%80%EC%9A%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">edge 지우는 방법</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#deadlock-avoidance-vs-detection\">📌deadlock avoidance vs detection</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#deadlock-recovery\">📌deadlock recovery</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#deadlock-termination\">📖deadlock termination</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#termination-cost-model\">termination cost model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#resource-preemption\">📖resource preemption</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#preemption-cost-model\">preemption cost model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#checkpoint-restart-method\">📖checkpoint-restart method</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"DeadLock 4","date":"2023년 02월 20일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-21-DeadLock-4/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-20-DeadLock-1/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"DeadLock 1","date":"2023-02-20 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-21-DeadLock-3/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"DeadLock 3","date":"2023-02-21 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}